33 seeks to represent.
34 (D) A certification that the candidate meets the qualifications
35 for candidacy imposed by this chapter.
36 (E) The school corporation district that the candidate seeks to
37 represent.
38 (2) Only eligible voters residing in the school corporation district
39 as provided in section 4.1 of this chapter may vote for a candidate
40 to represent that school corporation district.
41 (3) One (1) candidate shall be elected for each school corporation
42 district provided by section 4.1 of this chapter. The candidate
